lenders.name: Olivia Petrielli
lenders.occupational_info: Olivia Petrielli is a current senior who is finishing up her final semester of college at Illinois State University.  Olivia Petrielli is a hard-working and dedicated student, devoting a great deal of her time to her major in accounting.  This year, she has earned herself a position as a TA in accounting, and is a member of the Student Accounting Society at the school.  Olivia Petrielli is proud to be able to say she has maintained a GPA of 3.79 in her major, and will be attending graduate school following graduation.  She has recently been accepted to Roosevelt University in Chicago, where she will pursue her Master's degree in accounting.  Olivia Petrielli will start her Master's education by taking some classes online this summer, but will attend as a full-time student in the fall.
